        <item>
            <title>中大研发「液态磁控机械人」 减低手术风险及抗生素依赖</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/29/cuhk_microbot/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cuhk_microbot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/29/cuhk_microbot/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 05:30:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300106</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>细菌膜感染（Biofilm Infection）一直是医疗界的一大难题，尤其当感染出现在身体内的植入物（例如支架、导管或网状修补物）时，更难以清除，患者往往需进行高风险的手术或长期依赖抗生素治疗。</p><h2>中大领军研发液态机械人</h2><p>最近由香港中文大学（CUHK）领导的国际科研团队，开发出一种创新「液态磁控机械人」（Liquid-bodied Antibiofilm Robot），不仅能穿越复杂的医疗植入物表面，还可直接破坏细菌膜，并同时杀灭病菌。这款液态机械人由磁性水凝胶构成，内含微型磁性粒子。透过外部磁场的控制，它能自由改变形状，轻松穿过如支架或医疗网片等复杂结构的缝隙和表面。研究指出，机械人在磁场驱动下，可以透过机械力直接破坏细菌膜结构，同时释放抗菌药物，达到化学和机械双重抗菌效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f5-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f5-678x580.jpg" alt="" width="678" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f5-678x580.jpg 678w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f5-scaled.jpg 1052w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 678px" /></a></p><h2>主动捕捉防止再感染</h2><p>更值得一提的是，该机械人能「主动捕捉」被破坏后的细菌膜碎片，防止细菌再次扩散或重新感染。研究团队以人工培养的细菌膜进行测试，证实该机械人在短短数分钟内便能清除高达八成以上的细菌膜和病菌。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f4-scaled.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f4-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f4-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f4-scaled.jpg 830w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></a></p><h2>动物实验成效显著</h2><p>此外研究团队还透过猪胆管及老鼠的活体实验验证了此技术的可行性。在猪胆管测试中，液态机械人成功在内窥镜和 X 光追踪下，穿越复杂的金属胆管支架表面，清除了表面的细菌膜。在老鼠实验中，受细菌感染的植入支架在机械人治疗后，细菌数量明显下降，老鼠的体重和健康状况也比未治疗的对照组恢复得更快。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-652x580.jpg" alt="" width="652" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-652x580.jpg 652w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-1012x900.jpg 1012w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-scaled.jpg 1011w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 652px" /></a></p><h2>未来临床应用前景</h2><p>研究人员认为，这种创新技术未来有望广泛应用于临床，例如用于消除腹膜疝气修补网片、胆管支架、甚至心血管植入装置上的细菌感染，有效降低手术风险及抗生素滥用问题，为患者带来更安全、更有效的治疗方式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-652x580.jpg" alt="" width="652" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-652x580.jpg 652w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-1012x900.jpg 1012w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f3-scaled.jpg 1011w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 652px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f2-594x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f2-594x580.jpg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f2-scaled.jpg 922w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f1-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f1-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/sciadvadt8213f1-scaled.jpg 1213w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>资料来源：Science.org</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/29/cuhk_microbot/fun-tech/">中大研发「液态磁控机械人」 减低手术风险及抗生素依赖</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
